trans-unit.source: A service contract that defines the methods that wrap the Message-oriented operation contracts exposed by IWSTrustChannelContract.
trans-unit.target: Servicekontrakten som definerer metodene som bryte meldingen orientert operasjonen kontraktene eksponert i IWSTrustChannelContract.

trans-unit.source: Asynchronously sends a WS-Trust Cancel message to an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Asynkront sender en WS-Trust avbryte melding til et endepunkt.

trans-unit.source: An optional <xref:System.AsyncCallback> delegate, to be called when the send is complete.

trans-unit.source: A user-provided object that distinguishes this particular asynchronous send request from other requests.
